{"data": [{"id": "4742720", "title": "Hercules Capital: Are The Dividends Safe? I'm Buying!", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638002212/image_638002212.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Pomnik Alexander\" data-id=\"638002212\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1040px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638002212/image_638002212.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638002212/image_638002212.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638002212/image_638002212.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638002212/image_638002212.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638002212/image_638002212.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638002212/image_638002212.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638002212/image_638002212.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638002212/image_638002212.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">benjaminec/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Hercules Capital (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HTGC\" title=\"Hercules Capital, Inc.\">HTGC</a></span>) is a business development company concentrating on (mostly) US businesses operating within a few key sectors:</p> <ul> <li>Technology.</li> <li>Life sciences.</li> <li>SaaS.</li> <li>Sustainable and renewable technology.</li> </ul> <p>It offers attractive income to its shareholders (~10% yield</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638002212/image_638002212.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742720-hercules-capital-are-the-dividends-safe-im-buying", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 02:31:25"}, {"id": "4742719", "title": "Regeneron: Recent Bear Run May Be Justified -- Pharma Faces A Testing 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172413295/image_172413295.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"An up close picture of report card grades\" data-id=\"172413295\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172413295/image_172413295.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172413295/image_172413295.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172413295/image_172413295.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172413295/image_172413295.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172413295/image_172413295.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172413295/image_172413295.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172413295/image_172413295.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172413295/image_172413295.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">jaker5000</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Overview</h2> <p>So far this year, I have covered <b>Regeneron Pharmaceuticals, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/REGN\" title=\"Regeneron Pharmaceuticals, Inc.\">REGN</a></span>), the New York based Pharma giant, on two occasions. In <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4661781-why-i-expect-regeneron-to-keep-delivering-for-investors-in-2024-upgrade\">January</a>, I used detailed financial modelling to suggest that Regeneron stock was</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172413295/image_172413295.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742719-regeneron-recent-bear-run-may-be-justified-pharma-faces-a-testing-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 02:28:05"}, {"id": "4742718", "title": "MidCap Financial: 11% Yield, 86% Payout Ratio, NAV Discount (Upgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912018754/image_912018754.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businesspeople walking on painted up going graph, on asphalt\" data-id=\"912018754\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912018754/image_912018754.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912018754/image_912018754.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912018754/image_912018754.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912018754/image_912018754.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912018754/image_912018754.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912018754/image_912018754.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.