er-stock-is-cheap-even-as-shares-dip-in-post-earnings-period", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 01:37:32"}, {"id": "4742713", "title": "GE HealthCare: Growth Acceleration In 2025 Can Drive Stock Higher", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641146680/image_641146680.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"General Electric company logo on the headquarters building in Prague\" data-id=\"641146680\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4371px\" height=\"2914px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641146680/image_641146680.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641146680/image_641146680.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641146680/image_641146680.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641146680/image_641146680.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641146680/image_641146680.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641146680/image_641146680.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641146680/image_641146680.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641146680/image_641146680.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">josefkubes</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>GE HealthCare Technologies\u2019 (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GEHC\" title=\"GE HealthCare Technologies Inc.\">GEHC</a></span>) stock has been flattish since my <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4710844-ge-healthcare-encouraging-long-term-growth-prospects\">previous bullish article</a>. The Chinese growth headwinds were a major distraction for the company, which resulted in disappointing stock price performance in the recent quarters. However, I</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641146680/image_641146680.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742713-ge-healthcare-growth-acceleration-in-2025-can-drive-stock-higher", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 01:25:25"}, {"id": "4742711", "title": "Abandon Ship: Why Canoo Isn't Worth The Risk", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369945500/image_1369945500.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Group of young sup surfers fall from SUP stand up paddle board, women drowning, concept of fail solving problems, team work and survival, boat accident during stand up paddling, standup paddleboarding\" data-id=\"1369945500\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369945500/image_1369945500.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369945500/image_1369945500.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369945500/image_1369945500.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369945500/image_1369945500.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369945500/image_1369945500.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369945500/image_1369945500.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369945500/image_1369945500.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https: